      "content": "I don't really follow the metaphor, I'm just trying to get to Singapore. Regarding the hubs, the Doha and Dubai options seem more likely to have seats available, but I'm worried about the layover times increasing the total trip length. Can you compare the typical connection efficiency of those two hubs versus trying to find a direct one from a place like Frankfurt or Paris?",
